name: Confession II
description: He looked into the abyss and encountered the luminous darkness. Confessing paradoxes with HEN666 - Animated from the painting Saint Joseph and the Christ Child by Guido Reni, 1640. Poem is taken from Charles Baudelaire "The Denial Of Saint Peter" - Performed by Laurence Fuller @laurencefuller produced by Laurence Fuller and Logan Dennison @Unmastered_art
